# Animations

This folder will contain Lottie animation files and other animated assets for the Kooka app.

## Planned Animations

- Loading animations for AR content
- Button press feedback animations  
- Character animations for mascots
- Transition animations between screens

## File Formats

- Lottie JSON files (.json)
- GIF files for simple animations
- MP4 files for video backgrounds

## Usage

Animations will be used to enhance the magical and playful experience of the app while maintaining good performance.
